1. Create a Docker Command
Run the following command to start Adminer:

bash
Copy code
docker run -d \
  --name adminer \
  -p 8080:8080 \
  adminer

  
2. Access Adminer
Open your browser and go to http://localhost:8080.
Enter your database details:
System: PostgreSQL
Server: host.docker.internal (to connect to localhost)
Username: Your database username
Password: Your database password
Database: Your database name
